Ex-BBNaija season 4 housemate Omashola has welcomed a baby boy with fiancée. The media personality revealed this via an Instagram post on Tuesday where he shared a short clip in which he was seen opening and popping a bottle of champagne. It the post’s caption, Omashola made the announcement. He wrote: “It’s a boy.” This was several days after the reality TV star shared a video of his fiancée’s sonogram which displayed the baby’s movement in the womb.   Mercy Aigbe confirms marriage to ‘D owner’     Ekubo seeks ends to violence, abductions     My mother forced me to donate N200k as first fruit –…   - Advertisement - While Sholzy captioned the post, he noted he’d always thought his manhood wouldn’t be capable of impregnating a woman. “All these years, I was thinking my ‘pee pee’ doesn’t work. Finally, we got a very long leg start,” he wrote. The model began the New Year as an engaged man as he disclosed that he proposed to his girlfriend and she said yes. Omashola shared a clip of the underwater proposal on his Instagram page on December 31, 2021, and pointed out that it was the highlight of the year. He wrote: “2021 has a lot of secrets but my biggest highlight was when she said YES and the rest is history. Please don’t ask me what happened. Happy New Year.”